Estimate Flows, Sources, WAIFM, Flow ratios

source.attribution.aggmcmc.getKeyQuantities.Rd

Estimate Flows, Sources, WAIFM, Flow ratios

source.attribution.aggmcmc.getKeyQuantities(infile, control)

Arguments

infile

Full file name to aggregated MCMC output from function source.attribution.mcmc
control

List of input arguments that control the behaviour of the derivation of key quantities:

  • "quantiles"Named list of quantiles. Default: c('CL'=0.025,'IL'=0.25,'M'=0.5,'IU'=0.75,'CU'=0.975)

  • "flowratios"Cector of length 3. First element: name of flow ratio. Second element: name of transmission pair category for enumerator of flow ratio. Third element: name of transmission pair category for denominator of flow ratio.

  • "outfile"Full file name for output csv file.

Value

NULL. A csv file is written to disk.
